titleInfo.title: (PC) Turner v. Dickinson et al
titleInfo.subTitle: ORDER AND FINDINGS and RECOMMENDATIONS signed by Magistrate Judge Dale A. Drozd on 12/13/11 ORDERING that defendant's 10/05/11 32 Request for Clarification is GRANTED; defendant's answer shall be filed within fourteen days following any order by the assigned District Judge with respect to these findings and recommendations; and RECOMMENDING that: the second claim of plaintiff's 12 amended complaint be dismissed as duplicative; the third, fourth and fifth claims of plaintiff's amended complaint be dismissed for failure to state a cognizable claim; and this action proceed solely on plaintiff's first claim against defendant Dr. Rohrer for providing plaintiff inadequate medical care in violation of his rights under the Eighth Amendment. Objections to these F&Rs due within 21 days; referred to Judge Garland E. Burrell, Jr. (Benson, A.)
